      <li>Sample response: <ol>
<li>One of the 3 parts is shaded, which represents <m>\frac{1}{3}</m>. Each third can be split into 2 equal parts, making 6 parts. Two of the parts are shaded, which represents <m>\frac{2}{6}</m>.
