<img alt="Diagram." role="image" src="../../../../../../figures/tikz-file-158704.svg" width="80%"/>
</li>
<li>The diagram can be partitioned into 2 equal parts. Both parts are shaded, which represents <m>\frac{2}{2}</m>. Each half can be split into 3 equal parts, making 6 parts. All 6 parts are shaded, which represents <m>\frac{6}{6}</m>.
